 |автор         = Brian Betham Schofield.
 |заглавие      = The Arctic Convoys
 |ссылка        = http://books.google.com/books?ei=Y_XaTLftIMaAOo322MoJ&ct=result&id=uWIJAQAAIAAJ&dq=La+Malouine+PQ-17&q=La+Malouine#search_anchor
